Invocation Name: jackson county facts
des: Learn more about Jackson County North Carolina and discover little known facts. Plan your next trip today! Made up of Cashiers, Cherokee, Dillsboro and Sylva, Jackson County’s charming Western North Carolina mountain towns offer year-round outdoor experiences. As a gateway to adventures big and small, Jackson County is the perfect place to call home while exploring the Great Smoky Mountains and Blue Ridge Parkway.
